== BMC_ITSM7_Incident_Close
Closes a BMC ITSM7 Incident (Help Desk) record
The BMC ITSM7 Incident (Help Desk) entry is modified in the 'HPD:Help Desk' form

For more information, see the Detailed Description section below.

=== Parameters
[Incident Number]
  The Indident ID to close
[Status Reason]
  The status reason used.

=== Sample Configuration
Incident Number::	<%=@results['Create_Incident']['Incident ID']%>
Status Reason::         Automated Resolution Reported

=== Results
Support Company

=== Detailed Description
Incident (HPD:Help Desk form) is set to a Status of Closed with the
Status Reason provided.